♪ Go hard or go home ♪

17:34.250 --> 17:35.580
♪ Go, go ♪

17:35.580 --> 17:36.920
♪ What you wanna do? ♪

17:36.920 --> 17:38.920
♪ Go hard or go home ♪

17:38.920 --> 17:40.670
♪ Go home, go, go ♪

17:40.670 --> 17:42.170
♪ What you wanna do? ♪

17:42.170 --> 17:44.000
♪ Go hard or go home ♪

